# task-ledger. The round DOCUMENTS are committed on purpose: a task ledger with no history is
# just a scratch file, and reconstructing what a round contained three weeks later is exactly
# what it exists to prevent. Only the pointer to the current round is transient.
.agent/ledger/ACTIVE
.agent/ledger/.state/
